  Rodimus reacts quicly and jumps to the cover of his family, blocking the falling debris.
   
  Rodimus Prime: I'm fast enough to keep up with him. I'll be back. You two stay here. I love you.
   
  Rodimus transformes to vehical mode and speeds off after Waspinator with full thrusters!

maximals wouldn't give him any rewards for helping them.  When he 
heard Elita yelling he saw that it might be a good distraction.  He 
flew into the air and fired an explosive stinger over Nighlight and 
Elita's heads hoping to bring some debries down on them before he 
truned and flew away as fast as he could.
"Hydras reward Waspinator when Waspinator tell him where maximals 
are heheheh!" he said to himself.
